---
import Image from 'astro/components/Image.astro'
import Techbar from './Techbar.astro'
import UA from '../assets/UA.png'
import UW from '../assets/UW.png'
---

<div class="flex flex-col items-center my-20 max-w-5xl">
  <h1 class="text-center text-2xl p-4 font-bold">Career Journey</h1>
  <div class="flex flex-col p-6 rounded-lg">
    <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-2">
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl text-white font-bold mb-2">Web Developer</h2>
        <p>University of Arizona (University Analytics & Insitutional Research)</p>
      </div>
      <p class="mb-4">November 2023 - Present</p>
    </div>
    <p>
      I work as the sole web developer on the KMap project at the University of Arizona, a university-wide research
      knowledge mapping platform which aims to display research collaborations and networks across the university. I
      built features to support research workflows, including publication management with ORCID and AI-assisted parsing,
      a grant update review system, and customizable researcher profiles. I improved usability through persona based UX,
      flexible content editing, and end-user documentation modeled after Docusaurus.
    </p>
    <Techbar techs={['TypeScript', 'Next.js', 'Linux', 'MongoDB']} />
  </div>
  <div class="flex flex-col p-6 rounded-lg">
    <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-2">
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl text-white font-bold mb-2">IT Support Specialist</h2>
        <p>International Wood Products</p>
      </div>
      <p class="mb-4">May 2023 - November 2023</p>
    </div>
    <p>
      Given a return offer to International Wood Products, I returned in May 2023. Working at this company was fun and
      gave me unique opportunities. I've was called the data magic guy, for writing Python and Powershell scripts which
      save the team hours of manual work and labor, one of which automates a report for the accounting department that
      saves around an hour each day.
    </p>
    <Techbar techs={['Windows Server', 'Python', 'WordPress', 'Microsoft 365', 'ERP Migration']} />
  </div>
  <div class="flex flex-col p-6 rounded-lg">
    <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-2">
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl text-white font-bold mb-2">Hackathon Participant</h2>
      </div>
      <p class="mb-4">January 2023 - March 2023</p>
    </div>
    <p class="mb-2">
      Starting in January and continuing until March, I participated in my first few hackathons, these being the
      community-run TreasureHacks, and Major League Hacking sanctioned Transport and Whisker Hacks. Of these, a group
      project for TransportHacks, Package Tracker, took the award of best overall hack, while my project Picatso won the
      awards for best domain name and best use of Auth0.
    </p>
    <Techbar techs={['Next.js', 'React', 'Tailwind']} />
  </div>
  <div class="flex flex-col p-6 rounded-lg">
    <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-2">
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl text-white font-bold mb-2">IT Intern</h2>
        <p>International Wood Products</p>
      </div>
      <p class="mb-4">July 2022 - September 2022</p>
    </div>
    <p>
      My first ever internship, I helped the small information technology department for International Wood Products,
      the leading lumber and engineered wood products distributor in the Pacific Northwest. I learned a lot about
      hardware, Microsoft systems like Active Directory, and also spent a lot of time helping people around the company
      with technical issues and physical installations.
    </p>
    <Techbar techs={['Windows Server', 'Python', 'Hardware', 'Microsoft 365']} />
  </div>
</div>

<div class="flex flex-col items-center my-20 max-w-5xl">
  <h1 class="text-center text-2xl p-4 font-bold">Education</h1>
  <p class="text-purple-600">Go Huskies!</p>
  <div class="flex p-6 rounded-lg items-center gap-12">
    <Image loading={'lazy'} format={'webp'} alt={`University of Arizona`} src={UA} class={`h-min`} />
    <div class="flex flex-col">
      <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-2">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl text-white font-bold mb-2">Masters</h2>
          <p>University of Arizona (Software Engineering)</p>
        </div>
        <p class="mb-4">January 2025 - Present</p>
      </div>
      <Techbar techs={['Agile Methodologies', 'Computer Architecture', 'DevSecOps']} />
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="flex p-6 rounded-lg items-center gap-12">
    <div class="flex flex-col">
      <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-2">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl text-white font-bold mb-2">Bachelors</h2>
          <p>University of Washington (Geography: Data Science)</p>
        </div>
        <p class="mb-4">September 2019 - December 2022</p>
      </div>
      <Techbar techs={['Agile Methodologies', 'Computer Architecture', 'DevSecOps']} />
    </div>
    <Image loading={'lazy'} format={'webp'} alt={`University of Arizona`} src={UW} class={`h-min`} />
  </div>
</div>
